name: CLLocationPushServiceError.Code
desc: Error codes the location manager returns if starting to monitor for location push notifications fails.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: An error code that indicates the app was unable to start the location push service for an unknown reason.

items.name: case missingPushExtension
items.desc: An error code that indicates the app is missing a Location Push Service Extension.

items.name: case missingPushServerEnvironment
items.desc: An error code that indicates the app is missing an Apple Push Notification service (APNs) environment entitlement.

items.name: case missingEntitlement
items.desc: An error code that indicates the app is missing the entitlement it needs to use the location push service.
